{"tid":2193412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西班牙成為首個西歐國家累積新冠病毒病例突破50萬","createTime":"2020-09-07T23:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T00:00:33.000Z","uid":360777,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"caf5d0529c95c387656e91fad07c9e302d6781e4","tid":2193412,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:00:53.000Z","msg":"西班牙在剛過去的周末期間，新增超過2萬6千宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，是第一個西歐國家，累積病例突破50萬。<br />\n<br />\n英國衛生大臣夏國賢警告，假如國內年青人不遵守社交距離限制措施，可能出現新一波爆發，呼籲年青人切勿放鬆，否則一旦受感染，可能傳染長輩，威脅他們的生命。<br />\n<br />\n法國在24小時之內，新增超過4200宗病例，累積約32萬9千人受感染，歐洲第3多。法國在最近幾個星期，單日新增個案呈上升趨勢，估計與放寬限制措施及增加病毒測試有關。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯表示會在今個星期，向志願人士提供疫苗，有關疫苗已進入後註冊期的測試階段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548391-20200908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548391-20200908.htm&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=f6d797d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548391-20200908.htm&h=60ec11c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548391-20200908.htm</a>"},{"pid":"50ce3fa46bcc24dd04dc3d5d33e556b402dc3053","tid":2193412,"uid":177955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:41:40.000Z","msg":"<del>新冠病毒</del><span class=\"red\">武漢肺炎</span>"},{"pid":"b8299f74391c3c0bbc8421d3ca05733c3a83bf4a","tid":2193412,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"俄羅師疫苗得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c91ec872f48a661ba732e5f5748f100ee72271","tid":2193412,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T23:46:50.000Z","msg":"新你老母<br />\n冠你老母<br />\n新冠肺炎  ❎<br />\n武漢肺炎/支那肺炎/中共病毒/支那賤畜病毒 ✅"},{"pid":"adcf31a269f2eff420b80c3ab090679f36c610cb","tid":2193412,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":